original: Ljungars, Folke Torvid, praktiserande (läkare, Huskvarna, f. 8/5/06 i Skeg-rie, Malmöh. 1., av godsäg. Olof L. o. Ella Håkansson. G. 34 m. Inger Wennberg. Barn: Kerstin 35, Gunvor 37. — Stud:ex. i Norrköp. 24, med. kand. i Sthlm 29, med. Hc. i Lund 34. Div. förordn. v. klin. o. -sjukh. 35-36, prakt. läk. i Huskvarna sed. 37.
translated: Ljungars, Folke Torvid, practicing (physician, Huskvarna, b. 8/5/06 in Skegrie, Malmöhus län, the first child of estate owner Olof L. and Ella Håkansson. Married since 1934 to Inger Wennberg. Children: Kerstin, born in 1935, Gunvor, born in 1937. Educational background: Passed the senior secondary exam in Norrköping in 1924, graduated with a bachelor's degree in medicine in Stockholm in 1929, obtained a medical license (Hc.) in Lund in 1934. Held various appointments in clinics and hospitals from 1935 to 1936, practicing physician in Huskvarna since 1937.
